{"article_id":"deXAx2cmUyUIm00f","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The US House of Representatives voted on Wednesday to find former Internal Revenue Service official Lois Lerner in contempt of Congress","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"for refusing to testify about alleged IRS targeting of tea party organizations","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"seeking tax exempt status .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"The House also approved a measure","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"asking Attorney General Eric Holder to appoint a special prosecutor","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"to investigate the IRS case .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Republicans ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"who control the House ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"unanimously supported the measures ;","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"six Democrats voted to hold Ms. Lerner in contempt","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"and 26 voted to petition Mr. Holder for a special counsel .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"According to congressional rules ,","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"the contempt resolution does not need to go through the Senate .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"What does all this mean for Lerner , legally and politically ?","depth":2},{"id":14,"text":"1 . Legally , the point","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"of filing a contempt charge","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"is to compel someone to testify .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"\" We want her simply , simply to answer the questions , \"","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"said Rep. Jim Jordan","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"( R )","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"of Ohio from the House floor on Wednesday .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Representative Jordan is a member of the House Committee on Oversight and Reform","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"that has been investigating the IRS matter .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"A year ago , Lerner said at a gathering of the American Bar Association","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"that agents had improperly singled out tea party for extra scrutiny .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"The oversight committee then began investigating ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"calling Lerner to testify .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"But she asserted her constitutional right","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"to remain silent","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"by pleading the Fifth Amendment","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"that protects from self-incrimination .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"A legal argument has ensued about that plea .","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"Republicans say","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"that Lerner forfeited her right","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"to remain silent","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"because she first , in a brief statement , asserted her innocence .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"That amounts to testimony ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"they say :","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"It ' s then too late to plead the Fifth .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Democrats argue","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"that oversight chairman Darrell Issa","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"( R )","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"of California forfeited his right","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"to charge contempt","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"by closing down the hearing","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"without ever challenging Lerner ' s pleading of the Fifth .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"As a result of the contempt charge Wednesday , it will be up to a judge to decide who is right .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"2 .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"If a judge finds Lerner in contempt ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"she could face a fine of up to $ 100,000 and jail time of up to 12 months .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"That is ,","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"if it gets that far .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"First , the case has to be referred to a US attorney .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"But the Justice Department could decide","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"the charge is frivolous","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"and refuse to prosecute ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"says Craig Holman , a government affairs lobbyist for Public Citizen ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"which advocates for consumers .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"The House could also go to court","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"to attempt to compel Lerner to testify .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"If the contempt charge does get to a courtroom ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"Mr. Holman says ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"it ' s likely to be thrown out","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"because a judge will view it \" more as partisan politics . \"","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Republicans suspect","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"the IRS targeting was politically motivated","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"and that the White House may have been involved ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"but an inspector general ' s report found no evidence of either ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"nor have congressional probes .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"The fact","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"that the contempt charge is criminal","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"is another clue","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"that the case is political ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"Holman explains .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"The House did not need to go that far ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"he says .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"It could just as easily have brought a civil charge of contempt .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"3 . Expect the issue to linger through the election season","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"\" This entire resolution really is partisan in nature , \"","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"Holman asserts ,","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"and Democrats agree .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"`` Instead of passing bipartisan legislation","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"to create more jobs ,","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"reform immigration ,","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"raise the minimum wage ,","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"or address any number of issues","depth":15},{"id":86,"text":"that affect our constituents every single day ,","depth":15},{"id":87,"text":"House Republicans are spending this entire week","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"trying to manufacture scandals for political purposes , ''","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"said Rep. Elijah Cummings of Maryland , the top Democrat on the House Oversight Committee .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Republicans defend their concerns as legitimate .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"\" No one should have to worry ,","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"no one","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"- Republican , Democrat , libertarian or otherwise -","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"should ever have to worry about their political speech having them singled out by the IRS , ''","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"said Rep. Rich Nugent","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"( R )","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"of Florida .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"`` We should be alarmed about the conduct of the IRS , under the direction of Lois Lerner .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"We should be worried about that in the future","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"because that is the biggest single threat to America today . ''","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"Witch hunt or not ,","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"no federal agency intersects more directly with the American public than the IRS ,","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"and the issue ,","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"if kept alive ,","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"would serve as another Obama-punching bag for the midterm elections .","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"4 . You can meanwhile count on the special counsel request going nowhere .","depth":5},{"id":107,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"you care about","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"Special prosecutors cost time and money -","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"think special counsel Kenneth Starr and the Monica Lewinsky scandal .","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"At the same time , the Justice Department is not yet finished investigating the IRS case .","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"But much more than that , it ' s hard to imagine Holder following up on this request .","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"In 2012 , Congress voted to hold the attorney general in contempt","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"for withholding documents","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"related to the botched gun-running operation","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"known as \" Fast and Furious. \"","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"There ' s no love lost between Holder and Republicans in Congress .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":241,"left":134,"right":240,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":133,"right":13,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":133,"left":126,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":123,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":0,"right":122,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":3,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":130,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":128,"right":129,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":128,"left":127,"right":8,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":127,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":131,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":240,"left":166,"right":239,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":166,"left":142,"right":165,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":136,"right":141,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":135,"right":16,"relation":"same-unit","n